<strong>Purchase price of variations</strong> = the average purchase price for variations in this warehouse is calculated based on the purchase price saved in the variation data.<br>
<strong>Moving average price of a variation</strong> = the average purchase price for variations in this warehouse is flexibly calculated. In this case, the average purchase price is calculated with all incoming items, but not with outgoing items.<br>
The calculation methods are described in depth in the chapter <a href="/en/stock-management/new-incoming items#250">Identifying the purchase price</a>.</p></td>
