The stock has to be recalculated after all changes. This recalculation is carried out in the menu <a href="/en/stock-management/managing-stock">Stock » Stocks</a> by clicking on <strong>Recalculate stocks</strong>.<br>
The availability symbols are displayed according to the settings made in the section <strong>Online store icon</strong> in the menu <strong>System » Item » Availability</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
