<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Display code</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The barcode can also be displayed as an alphanumerical sequence of characters.<br>
<strong>below</strong> = the characters are placed below the barcode<br>
<strong>within</strong> = the characters are placed within the barcode<br>
<strong>do not show</strong> = the characters are not displayed</p></td>
